I don't believe you

624
01:33:42,817 --> 01:33:44,079
How can I convince you?

625
01:33:52,793 --> 01:33:53,760
Draw your sword

626
01:33:56,430 --> 01:33:57,522
You've misled Nameless

627
01:33:58,065 --> 01:34:00,556
You've ruined Sky
and the Kingdom of Zhao

628
01:34:01,002 --> 01:34:01,969
Draw!

629
01:34:05,906 --> 01:34:07,737
When we first met...

630
01:34:09,744 --> 01:34:11,143
I had to prove myself to convince you

631
01:34:14,482 --> 01:34:15,813
What can I do this time?

632
01:34:16,250 --> 01:34:17,842
Just draw your sword!

633
01:35:44,939 --> 01:35:46,463
Why didn't you fend off my sword?

634
01:35:47,942 --> 01:35:49,409
So that you'd believe me

635
01:35:57,585 --> 01:35:59,610
I always wanted to go home with you

636
01:36:05,226 --> 01:36:06,693
Sadly, it won't happen now

637
01:36:11,899 --> 01:36:13,389
Take good care of yourself

638
01:36:27,548 --> 01:36:29,106
Why didn't you defend yourself?

639
01:36:38,259 --> 01:36:39,692
Why didn't you defend yourself?

640
01:36:50,971 --> 01:36:52,404
Why didn't you?

641
01:38:04,578 --> 01:38:06,876
No more drifting, no more roaming

642
01:38:13,454 --> 01:38:15,422
I'm taking you home now

643
01:38:18,125 --> 01:38:19,524
Our home

644
01:39:34,835 --> 01:39:36,393
Your Majesty, permission to execute?

645
01:39:36,603 --> 01:39:39,663
Permission to execute?

646
01:39:40,708 --> 01:39:42,107
Your Majesty, permission to execute?

647
01:39:42,476 --> 01:39:45,570
Permission to execute?

648
01:40:05,432 --> 01:40:08,424
He conspired to assassinate Your Majesty

649
01:40:08,635 --> 01:40:09,966
Show no mercy!

650
01:40:10,137 --> 01:40:13,698
This is the law of Qin!

651
01:40:16,677 --> 01:40:18,440
To conquer all under Heaven

652
01:40:18,645 --> 01:40:20,704
the law must be enforced

653
01:40:20,948 --> 01:40:23,508
Set an example for the world!

654
01:40:25,519 --> 01:40:28,079
Execute him! Execute him!

